1954;;Dangerous Mission;;American;;Louis King;;Victor Mature, Piper Laurie;;thriller;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dangerous_Mission;;After a young woman, Louise Graham, witnesses the murder of a crime boss, she flees the city, deciding to hide out in Glacier National Park. She is followed by two men, Matt Hallett and Paul Adams, one of whom is a federal agent, who had sworn to protect her and bring her back as a witness, the other a ruthless killer, determined to murder her.